sentences: Maarja-Liis Ilus, sometimes better known by her performing name Maarja (born 24 December 1980) is an Estonian pop musician and presenter.
She has represented Estonia in the Eurovision Song Contest twice.
She was only 15 when she participated in the 1996 contest.
Läbi jäätunud klaasi, together with Rein Rannap (2006)
He Is Always On My Mind (2003)
